    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-07-09T07:40:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-07-09T07:40:00-05:00" n="262"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d262">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/1714.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-07-09T08:00:00-04:40">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 9, 1915—8 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Party of armed men have gone to bush from Macoris and small party got away from
                    here. Leonte Vasquez, brother of Horacio, <pb facs="0404" n="288"
                        xml:id="pg_288"/> has recently returned from the United States and is in
                    Puerto Plata. Vidal thought to have left New York City on the <hi rend="italic"
                        >Iroquois</hi> but if not his activities in New York should be investigated
                    with a view to arrest. The Government has made a considerable number of arrests
                    here and in Puerto Plata of conspirators against the public peace. Enforced
                    enlistment for the army also rigorously proceeding. The Dominican gunboat <hi
                        rend="italic">Independencia</hi> has left for northern points. Censorship on
                    cables and telegraph.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Johnson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
